snippet.title: maybe: Interactive Stories | My Dear Goddess Ep 1
snippet.description:
Before you lost all your powers and reincarnated as a human, you used to be the goddess of the Seol Empire. With the help of three charming men, will you be able to lift the curse on the kingdom and find true love?
.
.
Scenario by Sparky / Artwork by winny / Original Novels from NAVER SERIES (©Kanghee, enry)
.
